{"tid":1695420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［進化］今次香港人終於嗌啱咗！！！","createTime":"2019-11-05T15:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:20:08.000Z","uid":97436,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29f447e1c7bd55f510c14ff4ee149b4082d27d6e","tid":1695420,"uid":97436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"跪咗玻璃先<br />\n今日11月5號去咗會展睇方皓玟x陳拍乳音樂會<br />\n完場眾港豬贖罪嗌緊口號嗰陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突然聽到有手足大嗌<br />\n香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟蹤橫街頭咁多個月終於聽到有人嗌啱<br />\n雖然得好少人跟住手足嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係始終係好嘅開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人要繼續進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 想嗌 香港人 暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人 罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"508a3259651a8a83d56be43f941f7edd01cf9554","tid":1695420,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"人哋聽音樂會就話人地港豬"},{"pid":"924575f2d36102b2444c193d7fc591286ad7908b","tid":1695420,"uid":97436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"自推十連發"},{"pid":"0728cec0b7fa007d5399690aa9f6e8fa924fd2ba","tid":1695420,"uid":97436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"508a3259651a8a83d56be43f941f7edd